title: Australia To Promote National AI Plan At India AI Impact Summit 2026
summary_full: Australia is stepping up its global engagement on artificial intelligence, with Assistant Minister for Science, Technology and the Digital Economy Dr Andrew Charlton visiting India this week to participate in the AI Impact Summit.
